# 設計文件

## 概述

量化交易機器人採用雙核心微服務架構，以 Rust 構建高性能實時交易核心，以 Python 構建靈活的回測分析核心。系統通過統一的 JSON 策略格式實現跨語言策略共享，並提供 CLI 控制介面和 Discord 通知功能。

## 架構

### 整體架構圖

```mermaid
graph TB
    CLI[CLI 控制介面] --> Gateway[API Gateway]
    Gateway --> TradingCore[Rust 交易核心]
    Gateway --> BacktestCore[Python 回測核心]

    TradingCore --> ExchangeAdapter[交易所適配器]
    TradingCore --> RiskManager[風險管理器]
    TradingCore --> StrategyEngine[策略引擎]

    BacktestCore --> MathModel[數學模型引擎]
    BacktestCore --> RealDataEngine[真實數據引擎]

    ExchangeAdapter --> Binance[Binance API]
    ExchangeAdapter --> OKX[OKX API]
    ExchangeAdapter --> Bybit[Bybit API]

    StrategyEngine --> StrategyStore[(策略存儲)]
    DataManager[數據管理器] --> TimeSeries[(時序數據庫)]

    NotificationService[通知服務] --> Discord[Discord Bot]

    TradingCore --> DataManager
    BacktestCore --> DataManager
    TradingCore --> NotificationService
```

### 核心組件架構

#### Rust 交易核心架構
```mermaid
graph LR
    WebSocket[WebSocket 連接池] --> DataStream[數據流處理器]
    DataStream --> StrategyEngine[策略引擎]
    StrategyEngine --> OrderManager[訂單管理器]
    OrderManager --> ExchangeRouter[交易所路由器]

    RiskEngine[風險引擎] --> OrderManager
    PositionManager[持倉管理器] --> RiskEngine

    ExchangeRouter --> RestClient[REST 客戶端]
    ExchangeRouter --> WSClient[WebSocket 客戶端]
```

#### Python 回測核心架構
```mermaid
graph LR
    StrategyLoader[策略加載器] --> MathBacktest[數學模型回測]
    StrategyLoader --> RealDataBacktest[真實數據回測]

    MathBacktest --> MonteCarloEngine[蒙特卡羅引擎]
    MathBacktest --> NormalDistModel[正態分佈模型]

    RealDataBacktest --> DataProvider[數據提供商]
    RealDataBacktest --> MarketSimulator[市場模擬器]

    MathBacktest --> ReportGenerator[報告生成器]
    RealDataBacktest --> ReportGenerator
```

## 組件和介面

### 1. Rust 交易核心組件

#### 交易所適配器 (Exchange Adapter)
```rust
pub trait ExchangeAdapter: Send + Sync {
    async fn place_order(&self, order: Order) -> Result<OrderResponse>;
    async fn cancel_order(&self, order_id: &str) -> Result<()>;
    async fn get_balance(&self) -> Result<Balance>;
    async fn get_positions(&self) -> Result<Vec<Position>>;
    async fn subscribe_market_data(&self, symbols: Vec<String>) -> Result<MarketDataStream>;
