### 性能測試
```rust
use criterion::{black_box, criterion_group, criterion_main, Criterion};

fn benchmark_order_processing(c: &mut Criterion) {
    let mut trading_core = TradingCore::new();

    c.bench_function("process_order", |b| {
        b.iter(|| {
            let order = create_test_order();
            trading_core.process_order(black_box(order))
        })
    });
}

criterion_group!(benches, benchmark_order_processing);
criterion_main!(benches);
```

## 部署和監控

### Docker 容器化
```dockerfile
# Rust 交易核心
FROM rust:1.70 as builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .
RUN cargo build --release

FROM debian:bullseye-slim
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y ca-certificates
COPY --from=builder /app/target/release/trading-core /usr/local/bin/
CMD ["trading-core"]

# Python 回測核心
FROM python:3.11-slim
WORKDIR /app
COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install -r requirements.txt
COPY . .
CMD ["python", "backtest_server.py"]
```

### 監控指標
```rust
use prometheus::{Counter, Histogram, Gauge};

lazy_static! {
    static ref ORDERS_TOTAL: Counter = Counter::new(
        "orders_total", "Total number of orders processed"
    ).unwrap();

    static ref ORDER_LATENCY: Histogram = Histogram::new(
        "order_latency_seconds", "Order processing latency"
    ).unwrap();

    static ref ACTIVE_POSITIONS: Gauge = Gauge::new(
        "active_positions", "Number of active positions"
    ).unwrap();
}
```

這個設計文件提供了完整的系統架構，包括 Rust 交易核心、Python 回測核心、通用 JSON 策略格式、CLI 介面和 Discord 通知系統的詳細設計。

